NOTE ON OPTIONAL DEPENDENCIES: The optional `md` extra installs MDAnalysis, which
is licensed GPL-2.0-or-later. MDAnalysis is imported lazily and only when the MD
trajectory-bridge features are used; it is not part of the core dependency set, so
the core `pymol-mcp` package remains MIT-licensed. Distributing an environment that
bundles MDAnalysis may subject that combined distribution to GPL terms.
